{"tid":295591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"吳克儉：國民教育被「洗腦」兩字「扣死」","createTime":"2017-06-24T01:24:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T02:36:33.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d0f950e81297359fe936faa4b5e278baa966a3de","tid":295591,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T01:24:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170227/large/a0301a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170227%2Flarge%2Fa0301a.gif&h=2630016a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n教育局局長吳克儉出席電台節目時，回應國民教育爭議，形容好的措施最終被「洗腦」兩字「扣死」，認為大家應拿出證據，看看有沒有發生。<br />\n<br />\n吳克儉說，留意到社會近來對「洗腦」的看法有改變，外界以往會感驚恐，但現時聽到「洗腦」時會「皺一皺眉」，想一想誰人有能力可以「洗到個腦」。他認為，現時反國教只屬個別人士炒作，學界一直並透過多元模式推動國教。<br />\n<br />\n吳克儉提到，有指國民教育並無談及六四事件，但他說自己可指出哪本課本、哪個情節及有哪些老師因為教六四事件而獲頒行政長官卓越教育獎。<br />\n<br />\n任期即將完結，吳克儉說，超額完成教育政綱內容，但心情仍戰戰兢兢。至於任內有何失敗地方，吳克儉說有感政治凌駕教育，拖慢推動「一帶一路」東盟獎學金，令他感可惜。"},{"pid":"19567b1a3fde7d38bfd29fc91f4566e36a28e1db","tid":295591,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T01:24:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1338008-20170624.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1338008-20170624.htm&d=ZSAgWCCaSfSf8R%2BwuWmvq4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=c8a29f8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1338008-20170624.htm&h=ffa4273a\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1338008-20170624.htm</a>"},{"pid":"078cb28f97c98828013e34347ab1adff0bae8477","tid":295591,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T01:55:30.000Z","msg":"點解可以講咗一段嘢出嚟都係冇內容嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7ba10b5b71738e686ce106acc0cb48e042f4354","tid":295591,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike